"若你能克服前方的试炼，并最终获胜……你或许就能找到它。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:2924
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"ATLAS_EQUIPMENT_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK_PERFORMINGRITUAL_DIVINEREMNANTSPERFORMED_FINALE\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:2930
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"ATLAS_EQUIPMENT_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK_PERFORMINGRITUAL_DIVINEREMNANTSPERFORMED_FAILURE\"]/text"
msgstr "那最后一道和弦，虽从未奏响，却将永远以悔恨的形式，在你心中回荡。唉，仪式失败"
"了。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:2933
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"ATLAS_EQUIPMENT_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK_PERFORMINGRITUAL_DIVINEREMNANTSPERFORMED_FAILURE\"]/choice/text"
