#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:2939
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"ATLAS_EQUIPMENT_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK_PERFORMINGRITUAL_ULTIMACHALLENGEACCEPTED\"]/text"
msgstr "你将那神秘的坐标输入星舰数据库，准备动身追寻那该死的装甲，女杰与牧师的身影从"
"未离开你的脑海。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:2944
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"ATLAS_EQUIPMENT_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK_PERFORMINGRITUAL_CRYSTALLINECOMBATPERFORMED\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"……最终，它消退成典籍内散页发出的微弱光芒。其背面似乎蚀刻着某种地图，显示出一"
"个相对较近的位置……无从知晓那里有什么在等着你，如果有的话，但只有一种方法能查"
"明。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:2948
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"ATLAS_EQUIPMENT_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK_PERFORMINGRITUAL_CRYSTALLINECOMBATPERFORMED\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:2954
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"ATLAS_EQUIPMENT_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK_PERFORMINGRITUAL_AGEDFISHPERFORMED\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"……最终，它膨胀为震耳欲聋的刺耳噪音，迫使你痛苦地跪倒在地。你什么也听不到，除"
"了那铺天盖地的笑声。你什么也感觉不到，除了它嘲弄的语气。除了你内心深处一种新"
"生的、萌芽般的感觉……但，这究竟是什么感觉？在如此无助、挣扎的你，能分辨得清吗"
"？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:2956
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"ATLAS_EQUIPMENT_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK_PERFORMINGRITUAL_AGEDFISHPERFORMED\"]/choice[@req=\"DDHIDDENAUG_TRIBUTEMASK_CAGE\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "这感觉……是孤立无援。我冰冷，孤独，永陷牢笼。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:2958
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"ATLAS_EQUIPMENT_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK_PERFORMINGRITUAL_AGEDFISHPERFORMED\"]/choice[@req=\"DDHIDDENAUG_TRIBUTEMASK_CAGE\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你凝神锁定这份感受——这份与世隔绝的寒意——用尽你有限的力量，去盖过周遭轰鸣的狂"
"笑。你确实是孤独的。就算肉体上不是，精神上也已然如此——你这般转瞬即逝的存在，"
"永远无法拥有真正的陪伴。正是这份对真实自我的接纳，驱使你抬手抚向自己的脸庞……"
"\n"
"\n"
"……可你触碰到的，根本不是自己的脸。你只感受到更多同样绝望的情绪。或许这就是你"
"现在的全部。无论如何，你再也听不见那些笑声了。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:2962
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"ATLAS_EQUIPMENT_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK_PERFORMINGRITUAL_AGEDFISHPERFORMED\"]/choice[@req=\"DDHIDDENAUG_TRIBUTEMASK_CAGE\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_DDTRIBUTESHAPER\" and "
"not(@lvl)]/text"
msgstr "没错……这就是我内心深处最真实的模样。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:2964
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"ATLAS_EQUIPMENT_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK_PERFORMINGRITUAL_AGEDFISHPERFORMED\"]/choice[@req=\"DDHIDDENAUG_TRIBUTEMASK_CAGE\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_DDTRIBUTESHAPER\" and "
"not(@lvl)]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"刹那间，那股裹挟着你的诡异感被骤然撕扯而去，你所有的感官都迅速归位。你的塑贡"
"者站在你身前，端详着手中的一枚粉色面具——莫非是那张散页上的仪式召唤出了这枚贡"
"物面具，还强行让你戴上？又或者……那是你自己的选择？无论如何，这枚贡物面具，囚"
"笼之面，如今归你所有了……只是别再让你自己，或是你的船员，再次迷失在它所投射出"
"的痛苦之中。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:2967
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"ATLAS_EQUIPMENT_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK_PERFORMINGRITUAL_AGEDFISHPERFORMED\"]/choice[@req=\"DDHIDDENAUG_TRIBUTEMASK_CAGE\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_DDTRIBUTESHAPER\" and "
"not(@lvl)]/event/choice[@req=\"deeponecultist\"]/text"
msgstr "（深渊潜者信徒）让启蒙者的另一名成员戴上面具，成为塑贡者。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:2969
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"ATLAS_EQUIPMENT_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK_PERFORMINGRITUAL_AGEDFISHPERFORMED\"]/choice[@req=\"DDHIDDENAUG_TRIBUTEMASK_CAGE\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_DDTRIBUTESHAPER\" and "
"not(@lvl)]/event/choice[@req=\"deeponecultist\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你的塑贡者将面具交出，你看着第二名深渊潜者在面具之下，皮肤变得灰白。这暗沉的"
"色泽向外蔓延，逐渐覆盖了他们的大部分身躯，最终，他们与你的塑贡者变得一模一样"
"。你不确定成为启蒙者的长老是否真的如此简单，又或是这些面具还藏着别的秘密，但"
"你清楚一件事：仪式，至此完成。"

