#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:3070
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"ATLAS_EQUIPMENT_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK_PERFORMINGRITUAL_AGEDFISHPERFORMED\"]/choice[@req=\"DDHIDDENAUG_TRIBUTEMASK_DARK\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "这种感觉……是极致的恐惧。我双目失明，在黑暗中跌跌撞撞。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:3072
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"ATLAS_EQUIPMENT_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK_PERFORMINGRITUAL_AGEDFISHPERFORMED\"]/choice[@req=\"DDHIDDENAUG_TRIBUTEMASK_DARK\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你凝神捕捉这份感受——这份令人窒息的恐惧与焦灼的等待——用尽你仅有的力量，去盖过"
"周遭轰鸣的狂笑。你的确在蹒跚前行。就算肉体没有，灵魂也早已如此——你这般转瞬即"
"逝的存在，永远也找不到此生的出路。正是这份对真实自我的接纳，驱使你抬手抚向自"
"己的脸庞……\n"
"\n"
"……可你触碰到的，根本不是自己的脸。你只感受到更多同样焦灼不安的情绪。或许这就"
"是你如今的全部。无论如何，你再也听不见那些笑声了。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:3076
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"ATLAS_EQUIPMENT_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK_PERFORMINGRITUAL_AGEDFISHPERFORMED\"]/choice[@req=\"DDHIDDENAUG_TRIBUTEMASK_DARK\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_DDTRIBUTESHAPER\" and "
"not(@lvl)]/text"
msgstr "没错……这就是我内心深处最真实的模样。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:3078
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"ATLAS_EQUIPMENT_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK_PERFORMINGRITUAL_AGEDFISHPERFORMED\"]/choice[@req=\"DDHIDDENAUG_TRIBUTEMASK_DARK\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_DDTRIBUTESHAPER\" and "
"not(@lvl)]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"刹那间，那股裹挟着你的诡异感被骤然撕扯而去，你所有的感官都迅速归位。你的塑贡"
"者站在你身前，端详着手中的一枚灰黑白面具——莫非是那张散页上的仪式召唤出了这枚"
"贡物面具，还强行让你戴上？又或者……那是你自己的选择？无论如何，这枚贡物面具，"
"黯影之面，如今归你所有了……只是别再让你自己，或是你的船员，再次迷失在它所投射"
"出的惶惑不安之中。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:3081
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"ATLAS_EQUIPMENT_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK_PERFORMINGRITUAL_AGEDFISHPERFORMED\"]/choice[@req=\"DDHIDDENAUG_TRIBUTEMASK_DARK\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_DDTRIBUTESHAPER\" and "
"not(@lvl)]/event/choice[@req=\"deeponecultist\"]/text"
msgstr "（深渊潜者信徒）让启蒙者的另一名成员戴上面具，成为塑贡者。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:3083
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"ATLAS_EQUIPMENT_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK_PERFORMINGRITUAL_AGEDFISHPERFORMED\"]/choice[@req=\"DDHIDDENAUG_TRIBUTEMASK_DARK\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_DDTRIBUTESHAPER\" and "
"not(@lvl)]/event/choice[@req=\"deeponecultist\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你的塑贡者将面具交出，你看着第二名深渊潜者在面具之下，皮肤变得灰白。这暗沉的"
"色泽向外蔓延，逐渐覆盖了他们的大部分身躯，最终，他们与你的塑贡者变得一模一样"
"。你不确定成为启蒙者的长老是否真的如此简单，又或是这些面具还藏着别的秘密，但"
"你清楚一件事：仪式，至此完成。"

