#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:3192
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"ATLAS_EQUIPMENT_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK_PERFORMINGRITUAL_AGEDFISHPERFORMED\"]/choice[@req=\"DDHIDDENAUG_TRIBUTEMASK_PLAGUE\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_DDTRIBUTESHAPER\" and "
"not(@lvl)]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"刹那间，那股裹挟着你的诡异感被骤然撕扯而去，你所有的感官都迅速归位。你的塑贡"
"者站在你身前，端详着手中的一枚绿色面具——莫非是那张散页上的仪式召唤出了这枚贡"
"物面具，还强行让你戴上？又或者……那是你自己的选择？无论如何，这枚贡物面具，疫"
"腐之面，如今归你所有了……只是别再让你自己，或是你的船员，再次迷失在它所投射出"
"的腐朽之中。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:3195
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"ATLAS_EQUIPMENT_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK_PERFORMINGRITUAL_AGEDFISHPERFORMED\"]/choice[@req=\"DDHIDDENAUG_TRIBUTEMASK_PLAGUE\""
