msgstr "（深渊潜者信徒）让启蒙者的另一名成员戴上面具，成为塑贡者。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:3197
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"ATLAS_EQUIPMENT_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK_PERFORMINGRITUAL_AGEDFISHPERFORMED\"]/choice[@req=\"DDHIDDENAUG_TRIBUTEMASK_PLAGUE\""
