msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_SIDE_EFFECT_ROLL_LIST_DANGER\"]/text"
msgstr "当你离开这本异界典籍时，一股不祥的寒意席卷全身。你隐约意识到仪式出了问题，却"
"又说不清究竟是哪里不对。唯有时间，会给出答案……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:3730
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_SIDE_EFFECT_ROLL_LIST_DANGER\"]/choice/text"
