msgstr "抵达信标，你发现自己身处一片阴影之中……黑暗之神早已预料到你的到来。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4052
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_ONEHUMAN_ANDUNSTABLESOULS\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "调查。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4054
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_ONEHUMAN_ANDUNSTABLESOULS\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"身后突然传来一阵声响，吓得你猛地一跳——转过身，映入眼帘的竟是一名活人祭品。你"
"正准备将这当作黑暗之神又一次神秘莫测的安排，一个从未听过的声音却在你脑海中窃"
"笑起来：\n"
"\n"
"“哦……运气不太好啊，古怪的家伙？想要……再多一点吗？”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4059
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_ONEHUMAN_ANDUNSTABLESOULS\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我在听……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4061
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_ONEHUMAN_ANDUNSTABLESOULS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "“哦……你确实在听，对吧？那就……给我凑点东西出来，怎么样，嗯，听着的那位？”那声"
"音继续窃笑着，而你思忖着它那盲目的交易……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4063
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_ONEHUMAN_ANDUNSTABLESOULS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "按那古怪的声音所说，凑点“东西”出来。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4065
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_ONEHUMAN_ANDUNSTABLESOULS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "一阵不祥的笑声在你周围的房间里回荡……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4070
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_ONEHUMAN_ANDUNSTABLESOULS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4072
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_ONEHUMAN_ANDUNSTABLESOULS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "……随后一声雷鸣般的炸裂，你的废料消失了，一个不稳定的灵魂凭空出现——就在你新祭"
"品的身旁。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4075
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_ONEHUMAN_ANDUNSTABLESOULS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "哇，呃，谢谢？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4077
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_ONEHUMAN_ANDUNSTABLESOULS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“哦……慷慨的人。是我……应该感谢你才对。” 你周围的笑声短暂地变得喧嚣起来，又一个"
"不稳定的灵魂出现了，随后笑声戛然而止。那声音似乎消失了……但你已收获了它交易的"
"回报。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4086
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_ONEHUMAN_ANDUNSTABLESOULS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "拒绝它的交易。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4088
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_ONEHUMAN_ANDUNSTABLESOULS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "那令人不安的声音没有再多言，只是继续窃笑……最终，笑声平息，而你在等待超光速驱"
"动器充能的时间里——或许，谢天谢地——再无事端。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4101
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//ship[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_TWOHUMANS_FIGHT\"]/gotaway/text"
msgstr "那艘民用船跃迁离开了，你的祭品丢了。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4104
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//ship[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_TWOHUMANS_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr "那艘船四分五裂，你迅速回收了你能找到的东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4107
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//ship[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_TWOHUMANS_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4112
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//ship[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_TWOHUMANS_FIGHT\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr "敌方船员尽数死亡，你迅速回收了你能找到的东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4115
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//ship[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_TWOHUMANS_FIGHT\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4122
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_TWOHUMANS_FIGHT_MERCY\"]/text"
msgstr "星舰起火，他们绝望地呼叫：“好吧！好吧，行了，我们懂了！我们……是你的财产了……我"
"们登船，只求你……别杀我们……”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4124
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_TWOHUMANS_FIGHT_MERCY\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "这还差不多。欢迎登船，祭品。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4126
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_TWOHUMANS_FIGHT_MERCY\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "他们对你感到作呕。尽管如此，他们还是信守诺言，登上了你的星舰。先是驾驶员……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4130
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_TWOHUMANS_FIGHT_MERCY\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4132
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_TWOHUMANS_FIGHT_MERCY\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "……然后是他的同伴。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4139
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_TWOHUMANS_FIGHT_MERCY\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "祭品可没有第二次机会。杀了他们。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4145
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_TWOHUMANS_FIGHT_DESTROYEDLOSS\"]/text"
msgstr "没有一个平民活着留下可以作为祭品……可惜了。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4154
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_TWOHUMANS_THREATEN_RUNAWAY\"]/text"
msgstr "那些人类怒目而视：“你的……财产？你是个变态的怪胎，对吧？！我们得赶紧离开这儿！"
"”他们切断了通讯，引擎启动了……他们想逃！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4157
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_TWOHUMANS_THREATEN_RUNAWAY\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4163
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_TWOHUMANS_THREATEN_SUBMIT\"]/text"
msgstr "那些人类脸色变得煞白。他们看到靠自己逃出去的机会渺茫，于是屈服了，同意登上你"
"的星舰。先是驾驶员……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4166
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_TWOHUMANS_THREATEN_SUBMIT\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4168
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_TWOHUMANS_THREATEN_SUBMIT\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr "……然后是他的同伴。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4178
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_TWOHUMANS\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr "你的仪式将你引至此处。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4180
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_TWOHUMANS\"]/text"
msgstr "抵达信标，你发现自己身处一片阴影之中……黑暗之神早已预料到你的到来。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4183
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_TWOHUMANS\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "调查。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4185
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_TWOHUMANS\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你注意到一艘民用船正在靠近，他们看起来迷路了……这一定是你的祭品。他们一发现你"
"的星舰就发来呼叫：“嘿，嘿，你知道我们他妈的这是在哪儿吗？前一秒，我们还在正常"
"航行，周围都是星星，下一秒我们就到了……这儿……”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4188
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_TWOHUMANS\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "你现在是我的财产了。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4192
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_TWOHUMANS\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "这是，呃，属于联邦的禁区。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4194
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_TWOHUMANS\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你向平民解释，这里是联邦的实验性武器测试场，你必须护送他们离开这里……用你的星"
"舰。驾驶员拒绝了：“你在开玩笑吗？你知道这艘星舰花了我多少钱吗？我不会把它丢在"
"这里，然后等上三年让联邦最终处理完再还给我。我自己找路出去。”不过，另一个平民"
"接受了，并登上了星舰……你得到了你的祭品。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4204
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//ship[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_THREEHUMANS_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr "那艘船四分五裂，你迅速回收了你能找到的东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4207
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//ship[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_THREEHUMANS_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4212
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//ship[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_THREEHUMANS_FIGHT\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr "敌方船员尽数死亡，你迅速回收了你能找到的东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4215
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//ship[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_THREEHUMANS_FIGHT\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4222
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_THREEHUMANS_FIGHT_DESTROYEDLOSS\"]/text"
msgstr "海盗死了，但你的祭品也死了……可惜了。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4226
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_THREEHUMANS_FIGHT_CAPTUREDWIN\"]/text"
msgstr "海盗死了，他们的奴隶就归你了。通知他们换了新主人后，你强迫他们跟随你登上你的"
"星舰；一个……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4229
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_THREEHUMANS_FIGHT_CAPTUREDWIN\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4231
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_THREEHUMANS_FIGHT_CAPTUREDWIN\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr "……两个……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4234
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_THREEHUMANS_FIGHT_CAPTUREDWIN\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4236
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_THREEHUMANS_FIGHT_CAPTUREDWIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "……三个。你的祭品都齐了，准备出发。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4248
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_THREEHUMANS\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr "你的仪式将你引至此处。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4250
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_THREEHUMANS\"]/text"
msgstr "抵达信标，你发现自己身处一片阴影之中……黑暗之神早已预料到你的到来。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4253
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_THREEHUMANS\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "调查。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4255
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_THREEHUMANS\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"奇怪的是，映入眼帘的是一艘海盗船。他们也毫不掩饰，发来呼叫：“嘿嘿！你也是来给"
"你的黑暗之主，或者随便什么玩意儿找东西的吧？因为如果你想要东西，我们这儿可有"
"货。”海盗将镜头转向三名被捆绑堵嘴的人类。原来这是个奴隶贩子……他们正以几乎难以"
"置信的低价向你兜售他们的“货物”。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4258
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_THREEHUMANS\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "买一个人类奴隶。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4260
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_THREEHUMANS\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "你给了海盗们一小点废料，他们送过来一个人类奴隶作为交换。真的吗？没有耍花样？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4266
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_THREEHUMANS\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "再买一个人类奴隶。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4268
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_THREEHUMANS\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "你又给了海盗们一小点废料，他们又送过来一个人类奴隶。你本以为这个价格肯定有猫"
"腻……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4274
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_THREEHUMANS\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "买最后一个人类奴隶。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4276
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_THREEHUMANS\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你最后给了海盗们一小点废料，他们果然送过来最后一个人类奴隶。你听到他们在议论"
"：“这些狂热分子真是做生意的天才，我们从没有过这么大的需求！我们说不定还能再降"
"价，照样不亏！”所以，黑暗之神经常派它的追随者来这儿……有意思。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4284
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_THREEHUMANS\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "我够了。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4286
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_THREEHUMANS\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "你放弃再买奴隶。对收集到的祭品感到满意，你放过海盗，准备离开信标。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4292
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_THREEHUMANS\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "我够了。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4294
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_THREEHUMANS\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "你放弃再买奴隶。对收集到的祭品感到满意，你放过海盗，准备离开信标。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4300
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_THREEHUMANS\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "你不是来付钱买祭品的。用武力夺取！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:4302
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_THEHUNT_THREEHUMANS\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"海盗的反应比你预想的要激烈得多：“你在开玩笑吗？就这个价？你们这些狂热混蛋到底"
