#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11214
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_MUSEUMOFSECRETS\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr "你的仪式将你引至此处。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11216
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_MUSEUMOFSECRETS\"]/text"
msgstr "抵达信标处，你置身于一片暗影夹缝之中……据说威能水晶就藏在这里，但你在外边什么"
"也没看见。尽管无法解释，你却被一股力量牵引，走向那本异界之书……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11219
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_MUSEUMOFSECRETS\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "你上前查看那本异界之书。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11221
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_MUSEUMOFSECRETS\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"当你靠近异界之书所在的房间时，注意到有光芒从门缝底下渗出。推门而入，你发现书"
"本本身正散发着炽烈的紫色光辉，神圣非凡……你感觉它正在将你往它那里牵引。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11223
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_MUSEUMOFSECRETS\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "试着抵抗。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11225
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_MUSEUMOFSECRETS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "你竭力抵抗，可还是失败了。异界之书将你狠狠拽入，彻底吞噬，然后……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11227
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_MUSEUMOFSECRETS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "然后呢？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11229
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_MUSEUMOFSECRETS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你的名字是阿克索洛克，你是一名恐龙族，肩负着夺回本族神圣水晶的重任。据说，这"
"块水晶位于神秘的“秘物博物馆”内，这座建筑是由你们领地南方的恐怖鸟魔建造并维护"
"的。经过漫长而艰险的旅程，你终于抵达了博物馆的入口。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11233
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_MUSEUMOFSECRETS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "进入，万分谨慎地。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11235
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_MUSEUMOFSECRETS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"如果鸟魔发现你在偷偷摸摸地四处走动，它们肯定会穷追不舍；至关重要的是，你绝不"
"能被发现。现在置身博物馆内，你发现自己被无数的展品包围着；奇特的饰品、怪物和"
"人类的剥制标本、详细记录着早已逝去的战争与时代的目录……其中一件展品引起了你的"
"注意，标签上写着“恐龙族”。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11237
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_MUSEUMOFSECRETS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "进入展区。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11239
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_MUSEUMOFSECRETS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "尽管你是个身经百战的战士，但看到同胞被这样制成标本，还是让你备受打击。不过，"
"若想凯旋归乡，你必须坚持下去。水晶一定就在这附近的某个地方……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11241
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_MUSEUMOFSECRETS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续搜索。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11243
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_MUSEUMOFSECRETS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"展区诡异地向四周延伸，笔直的走廊却把你引回起点，向上的楼梯却通往下方，门扉让"
"你迷失方向……尽管此地疯狂混乱，但你知道为了族人必须保持坚强。就在你思念亲人和"
"家园之时，你看到了它……水晶，就放在一个金色的基座上！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11245
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_MUSEUMOFSECRETS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "抓起水晶！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11247
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_MUSEUMOFSECRETS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"当你把水晶从基座上拿起时，警报响起……鸟魔们来了！你迅速冲出这座疯狂的迷宫，朝"
"博物馆出口奔去。不幸的是，鸟魔们已在守候……它们挡在了你和唯一的出路之间。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11249
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_MUSEUMOFSECRETS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "冲向鸟魔！为了我的族人！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11251
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_MUSEUMOFSECRETS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"怀着原始的勇气，你冲向那些羽翼恶魔。你想着等待你归来的故土，想着你带着族人神"
"圣水晶归来时会为你欢呼的亲人们……你即将与鸟魔相撞，就在这时，突然间……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11253
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_MUSEUMOFSECRETS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "就在这时，突然间……？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11255
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_MUSEUMOFSECRETS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你被一股猛烈的力量从异界典籍中弹了出来，砰的一声脸朝下摔在地上……刚才到底发生"
"了什么？你刚才在异界典籍里面……？还没等你真正回过神来，其他实体也被从书中弹了"
"出来……食铁族？！这些难道就是故事里的“鸟魔”吗……？你刚要跑去拉响警报，却意识到"
"手里有什么东西……是效能水晶！尽管对其手段完全摸不着头脑，但你不得不承认，黑暗"
"之神确实知道如何上演一出好戏。现在，到了终场……准备自卫吧！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11285
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_GARDENOFREDEMPTION\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr "你的仪式将你引至此处。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11287
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_GARDENOFREDEMPTION\"]/text"
msgstr "抵达信标，你发现自己身处一片阴影之中……据说效能水晶就在这里，但外面什么也看不"
"见。虽然无法解释，你感觉被吸引到了异界典籍旁……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11290
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_GARDENOFREDEMPTION\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "你上前查看那本异界之书。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11292
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_GARDENOFREDEMPTION\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"当你靠近异界之书所在的房间时，注意到有光芒从门缝底下渗出。推门而入，你发现书"
"本本身正散发着炽烈的紫色光辉，神圣非凡……你感觉它正在将你往它那里牵引。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11294
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_GARDENOFREDEMPTION\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "试着抵抗。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11296
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_GARDENOFREDEMPTION\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "你竭力抵抗，可还是失败了。异界之书将你狠狠拽入，彻底吞噬，然后……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11298
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_GARDENOFREDEMPTION\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "然后呢？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11300
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_GARDENOFREDEMPTION\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你没有名字，但你深知自己是地球守护者，肩负着重夺一枚稀有水晶的使命，它是守护"
"地球的关键。如今水晶落入了你致命的敌人，赫克斯机械体手中。你已潜入他们一处基"
"地，传闻水晶就藏在救赎之园。出击的时刻，到了。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11304
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_GARDENOFREDEMPTION\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "你开始在救赎之园中搜寻那枚水晶的踪迹。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11306
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_GARDENOFREDEMPTION\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"这里是一颗对生命极度不友好的星球，救赎之园里盘踞的并非普通赫克斯机械体，而是"
"一群因沉迷神秘学被同类放逐的赫克斯机械体分支。如果水晶真的在这里，他们一定会"
"把它藏在某个神圣之地，方便进行祈祷与膜拜。可在救赎之园无边无际的植被中，你至"
"今没有发现任何值得留意的地方。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11308
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_GARDENOFREDEMPTION\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续搜索。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11310
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_GARDENOFREDEMPTION\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "藤蔓，草地……藤蔓，草地……藤蔓，草地，一棵巨树……啊，一棵巨树。也许那值得一探？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11312
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_GARDENOFREDEMPTION\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "调查那棵巨树。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11314
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_GARDENOFREDEMPTION\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"巨树根部周围散落着各式各样的小玩意儿和小饰品。一只六手机械手，锈迹斑斑、枯萎"
"干瘪……一把大型步枪，威力巨大但已损坏……然后，某个特别闪亮的东西吸引了你的目光"
"。就是它！是水晶！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11316
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_GARDENOFREDEMPTION\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "抓起水晶！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11318
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_GARDENOFREDEMPTION\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "当你把水晶从地上拿起时，脚下的地面震颤起来……六手机械意识到了你对它们圣地的入"
"侵。你得赶快返回你的星舰！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11320
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_GARDENOFREDEMPTION\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "跑向星舰！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11322
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_GARDENOFREDEMPTION\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你跑过藤蔓和草地，继续跑，再往前跑……直到，终于，你的星舰映入眼帘！就在你快要"
"抵达时，一个六手机械增援舱正好落在你面前几英尺处，把你震倒在地……舱门打开，几"
"个六手机械俯视着躺在地上毫无防备的你。武器瞄准，每个六手机械都扣动了扳机，然"
"后……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11324
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_GARDENOFREDEMPTION\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "它们扣动了扳机，然后……？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11326
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFPOTENCY_GARDENOFREDEMPTION\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你被一股猛烈的力量从异界典籍中弹了出来，砰的一声脸朝下摔在地上……刚才到底发生"
"了什么？你刚才在异界典籍里面……？还没等你真正回过神来，其他实体也被从书中弹了"
"出来……分离者？！这些难道就是故事里的“六手机械”吗……？你刚要跑去拉响警报，却意"
"识到手里有什么东西……是效能水晶！尽管对其手段完全摸不着头脑，但你不得不承认，"
"黑暗之神确实知道如何上演一出好戏。现在，到了终场……准备自卫吧！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11356
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFHANDINESS_JUNGLEOFSAVAGERY\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr "你的仪式将你引至此处。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11358
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFHANDINESS_JUNGLEOFSAVAGERY\"]/text"
msgstr "抵达信标，你发现自己身处一片阴影之中……据说便携水晶就在这里，但外面什么也看不"
"见。虽然无法解释，你感觉被吸引到了异界典籍旁……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11361
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFHANDINESS_JUNGLEOFSAVAGERY\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "你上前查看那本异界之书。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11363
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFHANDINESS_JUNGLEOFSAVAGERY\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"当你靠近异界之书所在的房间时，注意到有光芒从门缝底下渗出。推门而入，你发现书"
"本本身正散发着炽烈的紫色光辉，神圣非凡……你感觉它正在将你往它那里牵引。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11365
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFHANDINESS_JUNGLEOFSAVAGERY\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "试着抵抗。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11367
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFHANDINESS_JUNGLEOFSAVAGERY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "你试图抗拒，但……失败了。异界典籍将你吸入，吞噬了你，然后……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11369
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFHANDINESS_JUNGLEOFSAVAGERY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "然后？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11371
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFHANDINESS_JUNGLEOFSAVAGERY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你的名字是查鲁斯，你是一名鸟魔，奉你神明之命去偷取被称为恐龙族的原始蜥蜴人的"
"一件神圣遗物。你的神明已向你揭示了水晶的位置：位于恐龙族“蛮荒丛林”深处的一座"
"神殿顶端。你躺在丛林边缘，准备去做你必须做的事。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11375
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFHANDINESS_JUNGLEOFSAVAGERY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "进入蛮荒丛林。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11377
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFHANDINESS_JUNGLEOFSAVAGERY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"在穿越茂密的树林、涉过比你还高的草丛时，你回想着关于此地的传说。据说有一条巨"
"蛇会从地底升起，吞噬任何胆敢闯入者，但……你并不觉得被特别“吞噬”了。除了被蚊子"
"咬。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11379
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFHANDINESS_JUNGLEOFSAVAGERY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续前行。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11381
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFHANDINESS_JUNGLEOFSAVAGERY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你正在砍开一片藤蔓丛，突然一声刺耳的咆哮从丛林更深处传来……虽然你知道距离尚远"
"，但发出这声音的生物一定无比巨大。你一边想着这个，一边穿过藤蔓丛，然后……你看"
"到了它！那座神殿！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11383
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFHANDINESS_JUNGLEOFSAVAGERY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "接近神殿。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11385
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFHANDINESS_JUNGLEOFSAVAGERY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"恐龙族或许野蛮，但在建造纪念物方面毫不含糊。那座神殿，一座宏伟的金字塔，顶端"
"是神圣的内室，直插云霄……仿佛在向星辰宣告。据你的神明所说，水晶就在神殿顶端的"
"那个内室里。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11387
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFHANDINESS_JUNGLEOFSAVAGERY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "开始攀爬。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11389
