"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFHANDINESS_JUNGLEOFSAVAGERY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"攀登异常艰辛，你希望自己族群的名字别这么讽刺……要是能直接飞到顶端就好了。感觉"
"爬了不知多少个小时，你终于到达了目的地：神殿的神圣内室。你走了进去，发现这里"
"无人看守……确实，一个金色基座上就放着水晶！你的神明或许会奖励你……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11391
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFHANDINESS_JUNGLEOFSAVAGERY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "抓起水晶！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11393
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFHANDINESS_JUNGLEOFSAVAGERY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"将水晶从基座上取下，神殿震颤起来……接着，你又听到一声令人毛骨悚然的咆哮。这次"
"，近多了……你得赶快离开这里！你迅速离开内室，但……已经太晚了。看来传说是真的。"
"你面前展现出比你见过的世间任何景象都更宏伟的一幕……一条真正的巨蛇。它的头颅甚"
"至举得比神殿顶端还高，身体盘绕数百英尺，延伸到丛林深处。它来这里惩罚你这个闯"
"入者，你别无选择，只能接受命运。巨蛇向后扬起头，摆出攻击姿态……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11395
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFHANDINESS_JUNGLEOFSAVAGERY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "它摆出攻击姿态，然后……？"

