"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFHANDINESS_LAKESOFRAGE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "追踪水晶的下落。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11448
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFHANDINESS_LAKESOFRAGE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "根据你的扫描仪，你离它不远了……但是，你的扫描仪也探测到了该区域有生命迹象。简"
"报里可没提这个，这颗行星现在应该是无人居住的……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11450
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFHANDINESS_LAKESOFRAGE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续前进。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11452
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFHANDINESS_LAKESOFRAGE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你只能希望这些生命是原始的，并且没有敌意……你承担不起空手而归的后果。跟随扫描"
"仪，你跋涉穿过黑曜石平原，进入了一片熔岩间歇泉区。这些间歇泉巨大而猛烈，将熔"
"岩喷射到数百英尺的高空……你在穿过时必须极其小心。一步算错，你就可能被活埋并被"
"烧成焦炭。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11454
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFHANDINESS_LAKESOFRAGE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "小心地穿过熔岩间歇泉区。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11456
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFHANDINESS_LAKESOFRAGE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他们称之为“怒火之湖”还真不是开玩笑；你从未见过无生命的东西看起来如此愤怒。穿"
"过这片区域时，你发誓那些喷发的间歇泉几乎感觉是冲着你来的……仿佛你脚下的土地都"
"憎恨你的存在。相对安全地离开后，你的扫描仪显示水晶就在前方，在这座火成岩山丘"
"的另一边……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11458
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFHANDINESS_LAKESOFRAGE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "翻过山丘。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11460
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFHANDINESS_LAKESOFRAGE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "在山顶上，你看到了它……水晶！虽然它微微嵌在山体中，但你确信能把它撬出来。你只"
"需这么做……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11462
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFHANDINESS_LAKESOFRAGE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "把水晶从地里撬出来。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11464
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFHANDINESS_LAKESOFRAGE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你用尽全力一拔，水晶松动了！然而，你的庆祝戛然而止，脚下的地面震颤起来……熔岩"
"从岩石中喷涌而出，从这些 plume 中升起了翻腾的、看似……有知觉的熔岩团块。确实，"
"这些熔岩魔像朝你逼近，虽然缓慢，但你意识到自己已被四面八方包围！简报里可一个"
"字都没提这些！你要死在这里了，被这颗星球本身杀死，而这一切都因为某个愚蠢的公"
"司连基本的安全程序都不执行！熔岩魔像现在高高耸立在你面前，其中一个抬起它巨大"
"的熔岩手臂砸下，你准备迎接命运，然后……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11466
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFHANDINESS_LAKESOFRAGE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "手臂砸下，然后……？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11468
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFHANDINESS_LAKESOFRAGE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你被一股猛烈的力量从异界典籍中弹了出来，砰的一声脸朝下摔在地上……刚才到底发生"
"了什么？你刚才在异界典籍里面……？还没等你真正回过神来，其他实体也被从书中弹了"
"出来……燃灵？！这些难道就是故事里的“熔岩魔像”吗……？你刚要跑去拉响警报，却意识"
"到手里有什么东西……是便携水晶！尽管对其手段完全摸不着头脑，但你不得不承认，黑"
"暗之神确实知道如何上演一出好戏。现在，到了终场……准备自卫吧！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11498
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFRAINBOWS_NIGHTMAREOFNONSENSE\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr "你的仪式将你引至此处。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11500
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFRAINBOWS_NIGHTMAREOFNONSENSE\"]/text"
msgstr "抵达信标，你发现自己身处一片阴影之中……据说虹彩水晶就在这里，但外面什么也看不"
"见。虽然无法解释，你感觉被吸引到了异界典籍旁……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11503
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFRAINBOWS_NIGHTMAREOFNONSENSE\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "检查异界典籍。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11505
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFRAINBOWS_NIGHTMAREOFNONSENSE\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"当你靠近异界之书所在的房间时，注意到有光芒从门缝底下渗出。推门而入，你发现书"
"本本身正散发着炽烈的紫色光辉，神圣非凡……你感觉它正在将你往它那里牵引。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11507
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFRAINBOWS_NIGHTMAREOFNONSENSE\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "试着抵抗。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11509
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFRAINBOWS_NIGHTMAREOFNONSENSE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "你试图抗拒，但……失败了。异界典籍将你吸入，吞噬了你，然后……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11511
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFRAINBOWS_NIGHTMAREOFNONSENSE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "然后？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11513
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFRAINBOWS_NIGHTMAREOFNONSENSE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "你的名字是皮特，多么甜蜜的名字！你只凭一把手枪，寻求那水晶！这就是我们的“荒诞"
"噩梦”！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11517
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFRAINBOWS_NIGHTMAREOFNONSENSE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我仅凭一把手枪，寻求那水晶！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11519
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFRAINBOWS_NIGHTMAREOFNONSENSE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "在这片美丽的土地，你不知它在哪里……那里！是水晶史蒂夫，带着一堆要搬运的货物！"
"这就是我们的“荒诞噩梦”！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11521
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFRAINBOWS_NIGHTMAREOFNONSENSE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "是水晶史蒂夫，带着一堆要搬运的货物！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11523
