"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFRAINBOWS_NIGHTMAREOFNONSENSE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "你用言语编织，恳求这位史蒂夫，哦！你多么渴望得到水晶！这就是我们的“荒诞噩梦”"
