"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFRAINBOWS_NIGHTMAREOFNONSENSE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你被一股猛烈的力量从异界典籍中弹了出来，砰的一声脸朝下摔在地上……刚才到底发生"
