#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11582
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFRAINBOWS_SEAOFSOLITUDE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "然后？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11584
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFRAINBOWS_SEAOFSOLITUDE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你的名字是赛瑟斯，你是一名学者。你被判处终身监禁于“孤独之海”，那是一个由冰雪"
"组成的非字面意义上的海洋，四周被字面意义上的冰海所包围。你被判刑的罪行——谋杀"
"你的妻子——并非你所为。你知道真正的罪犯……为了将他们绳之以法，你需要逃出这座监"
"狱，而你知道该怎么做。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11588
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFRAINBOWS_SEAOFSOLITUDE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "思考计划。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11590
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFRAINBOWS_SEAOFSOLITUDE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"监狱下方隐藏着一个隧道和通道系统。据说隧道内藏有一颗拥有难以想象力量的水晶，"
"最初是由远古时代的一个部落民族封印的……你只需找到它。有了它，在你逃脱时，任何"
"守卫或狱卒都无法阻止你。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11592
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFRAINBOWS_SEAOFSOLITUDE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "现在只需进入隧道……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11594
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFRAINBOWS_SEAOFSOLITUDE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "入口处通常无人看守……大多数人会冻死。但你并非大多数人，你是一名精通各种魔法的"
"学者。手持魔法火焰，你准备冒险进入隧道系统……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11596
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFRAINBOWS_SEAOFSOLITUDE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "进入隧道。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11598
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFRAINBOWS_SEAOFSOLITUDE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "你在隧道中穿行并非一帆风顺，但对付几个冰元素还是绰绰有余的。你应该很快就能接"
"近水晶了……必须继续前进。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11600
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFRAINBOWS_SEAOFSOLITUDE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "深入。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11602
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFRAINBOWS_SEAOFSOLITUDE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"深入到隧道系统深处，你最终在墙上发现了一个印记……这是水晶古老封印的残余。一定"
"是这里了！冲上前去，果然，你看到了它；水晶就在那里，等待你取走它，去开创你的"
"命运！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11604
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFRAINBOWS_SEAOFSOLITUDE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "抓起水晶！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11606
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFRAINBOWS_SEAOFSOLITUDE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"当你抓住水晶时，周围风声呼啸……洞穴里的空气通常不会呼啸，尤其是在这么深的地方"
"。转过身，你发现墙上的印记开始发光，那些你以为是纯粹装饰的古老水晶构造体，从"
"沉睡中苏醒了！构造体现在向你移动，准备保卫水晶……你得用你的魔法造诣击退它们！"
"你调动全身的力量，引导一个毁灭性的法术，这个法术……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11608
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFRAINBOWS_SEAOFSOLITUDE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我引导一个毁灭性的法术，这个法术……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11610
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFRAINBOWS_SEAOFSOLITUDE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你被一股猛烈的力量从异界典籍中弹了出来，砰的一声脸朝下摔在地上……刚才到底发生"
"了什么？你刚才在异界典籍里面……？还没等你真正回过神来，其他实体也被从书中弹了"
"出来……水晶族？！这些难道就是故事里的“构造体”吗……？你刚要跑去拉响警报，却意识"
"到手里有什么东西……是虹彩水晶！尽管对其手段完全摸不着头脑，但你不得不承认，黑"
"暗之神确实知道如何上演一出好戏。现在，到了终场……准备自卫吧！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11640
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFMARTYRDOM_PLAINSOFPERPETUITY\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr "你的仪式将你引至此处。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11642
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFMARTYRDOM_PLAINSOFPERPETUITY\"]/text"
msgstr "抵达信标，你发现自己身处一片阴影之中……据说殉道水晶就在这里，但外面什么也看不"
"见。虽然无法解释，你感觉被吸引到了异界典籍旁……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11645
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFMARTYRDOM_PLAINSOFPERPETUITY\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "检查异界典籍。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11647
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFMARTYRDOM_PLAINSOFPERPETUITY\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"当你靠近异界之书所在的房间时，注意到有光芒从门缝底下渗出。推门而入，你发现书"
"本本身正散发着炽烈的紫色光辉，神圣非凡……你感觉它正在将你往它那里牵引。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11649
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFMARTYRDOM_PLAINSOFPERPETUITY\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "试着抵抗。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11651
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFMARTYRDOM_PLAINSOFPERPETUITY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "你试图抗拒，但……失败了。异界典籍将你吸入，吞噬了你，然后……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11653
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFMARTYRDOM_PLAINSOFPERPETUITY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "然后？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11655
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFMARTYRDOM_PLAINSOFPERPETUITY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "你是莱拉克，如命运所昭示，你是这个世界的英雄。传说中的水晶将由你的手取得，让"
"时间得以恢复。你将不再需要生活在“永恒平原”，而是走向更伟大的……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11659
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFMARTYRDOM_PLAINSOFPERPETUITY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我真的……？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11661
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFMARTYRDOM_PLAINSOFPERPETUITY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"至少，你的导师是这么告诉你的。你某天醒来，失去了记忆。然而，你周围的每个人似"
"乎都证实了这一点……你别无选择，只能相信自己就是这位传说中的选召者。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11663
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFMARTYRDOM_PLAINSOFPERPETUITY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "准备出发寻找水晶。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11665
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFMARTYRDOM_PLAINSOFPERPETUITY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "你召集了一支队伍，包括你自己和另外四人，踏上了旅程。离开最后的庇护所——世界上"
"仅存的城市“堡垒”后，你无法预知会遇到怎样恐怖的怪物……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11667
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFMARTYRDOM_PLAINSOFPERPETUITY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "时间跳跃。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11669
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFMARTYRDOM_PLAINSOFPERPETUITY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "你们的五人队伍现在只剩四人。一头巨兽袭击了队伍，带走了你的导师……但你必须继续"
"前行。这是他们希望的，况且你现在也无法回头了。你必须找到水晶。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11671
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFMARTYRDOM_PLAINSOFPERPETUITY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "时间跳跃，再一次。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11673
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFMARTYRDOM_PLAINSOFPERPETUITY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你孤身一人。你站在倒下的同伴们的尸体旁，他们为了赢得这场战斗牺牲了一切。为了"
"拯救世界。向前走去，越过刚刚倒下的“遗忘之王”，你看到了它……你为之牺牲了一切所"
"知所识的水晶。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11675
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFMARTYRDOM_PLAINSOFPERPETUITY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "拿走水晶。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11677
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFMARTYRDOM_PLAINSOFPERPETUITY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"水晶在你手中，你感觉时间……在倒流。不，它不该倒流，它应该……你是莱拉克，如命运"
"所昭示，你是这个世界的英雄。传说中的水晶将由你的手取得，让时间得以……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11679
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFMARTYRDOM_PLAINSOFPERPETUITY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "让时间得以……？"

