msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFMARTYRDOM_GRAVEYARDOFDRAGONS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你的名字是卢卡斯，你是一个没有职业，但拥有信念的人。你随身带着一口棺材，里面"
"装着一块死去已久的神明的尸块，那个神明的存在曾几乎导致整个多元宇宙的毁灭。带"
"着它，你试图在“巨龙之墓”中再杀一个神。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11730
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFMARTYRDOM_GRAVEYARDOFDRAGONS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "漫步于墓园。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11732
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFMARTYRDOM_GRAVEYARDOFDRAGONS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"虽然并非字面意义上巨龙的安息之地，“巨龙之墓”这个名字仍然非常贴切：这里是众神"
"陨落的地方。你将在这里迫使“永生之神”现身，并随后将其杀死。人们将不再被诅咒永"
"远活下去。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11734
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFMARTYRDOM_GRAVEYARDOFDRAGONS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续漫步。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11736
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFMARTYRDOM_GRAVEYARDOFDRAGONS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "你只需找到一个合适的地点……比如前方的那片原野。预感到什么，棺材在锁链中晃动……"
"即使是死去的众神，体内也仍存有战斗的意志。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11738
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFMARTYRDOM_GRAVEYARDOFDRAGONS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "接近那片灰烬原野。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11740
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFMARTYRDOM_GRAVEYARDOFDRAGONS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "你能感觉到空气中有一股能量，仿佛大地本身也在激动地颤抖。你的脚步所到之处，灰"
"烬中盛开出花朵……稍纵即逝的生命是多么美丽啊。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11742
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFMARTYRDOM_GRAVEYARDOFDRAGONS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "躺在灰烬中，紧挨着棺材。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11744
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFMARTYRDOM_GRAVEYARDOFDRAGONS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "当你躺下时，草丛长出为你垫底……然后是花朵、灌木和藤蔓……生命本身也急切地加速。"
"是时候了。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11746
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFMARTYRDOM_GRAVEYARDOFDRAGONS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "打开棺材。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11748
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFMARTYRDOM_GRAVEYARDOFDRAGONS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"一片森林从棺材内蓬勃而出，树枝伸向天空，一阵嘈杂的声响迸发出来。就是这样……生"
"命孕育死亡。当现实自我撕裂，你目睹生命的死亡，你最后一次伸手去拿你的项链。那"
"是个简单的饰品；一根绳子，系着一块水晶……但它对你意义非凡。当颜色从树木、草地"
"、花朵、藤蔓、天空中褪去……你紧握住这块水晶，然后……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11750
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFMARTYRDOM_GRAVEYARDOFDRAGONS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我紧握住这块水晶，然后……？"

