"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFAURAS_REALMOFKNIGHTHOOD\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "试着抵抗。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11793
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFAURAS_REALMOFKNIGHTHOOD\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "你试图抗拒，但……失败了。异界典籍将你吸入，吞噬了你，然后……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11795
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFAURAS_REALMOFKNIGHTHOOD\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "然后？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11797
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFAURAS_REALMOFKNIGHTHOOD\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你的名字是熵，你是一位神祇。你走在骑士国度的一条林间小径上，小径的尽头是一间"
"小屋……小屋的地下室里有一块水晶。你来这里就是为了拿走它。如果拿不到，世界就会"
"毁灭。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11801
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFAURAS_REALMOFKNIGHTHOOD\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续沿小径前行。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11803
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFAURAS_REALMOFKNIGHTHOOD\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "从树林中走出，你看到了它：那间小屋。你将在这里拯救世界。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11805
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFAURAS_REALMOFKNIGHTHOOD\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "进入小屋。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11807
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFAURAS_REALMOFKNIGHTHOOD\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "小屋内有一扇通往地下室的门。门旁的桌子上放着一杯冰沙。如果你想成功，你需要它"
"。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11809
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFAURAS_REALMOFKNIGHTHOOD\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "拿起冰沙，进入地下室。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11811
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFAURAS_REALMOFKNIGHTHOOD\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "手握冰沙，你悄悄走下地下室的台阶……你听到水晶在呼唤你，“哦。原来如此。这是要直"
"接省去客套，直奔喝冰沙的主题了，是吗？”听起来……有些恼火。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11813
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFAURAS_REALMOFKNIGHTHOOD\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "是啊，好像我听不出来似的。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11815
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFAURAS_REALMOFKNIGHTHOOD\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "嘿，评论这些好歹也是我的工作！呃，你走下地下室楼梯，水晶就在那里。你握紧了手"
"中的冰沙。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11817
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFAURAS_REALMOFKNIGHTHOOD\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "抓起水晶。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11819
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFAURAS_REALMOFKNIGHTHOOD\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"是的，谢谢你！你走向水晶，喝下冰沙，然后抓住了它。水晶就那样躺在那里，被你抓"
"住了。你没想到会这么容易。然后，巨大的昆虫从背后袭击了你，等等，什么？这根本"
"说不……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11821
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFAURAS_REALMOFKNIGHTHOOD\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "这根本说不……？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11823
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFAURAS_REALMOFKNIGHTHOOD\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你被一股猛烈的力量从异界典籍中弹了出来，砰的一声脸朝下摔在地上……刚才到底发生"
"了什么？你刚才在异界典籍里面……？还没等你真正回过神来，其他实体也被从书中弹了"
"出来……螳螂族？！这些难道就是故事里的“巨大昆虫”吗……？你刚要跑去拉响警报，却意"
"识到手里有什么东西……是光环水晶！尽管对其手段完全摸不着头脑，但你不得不承认，"
"黑暗之神确实知道如何上演一出好戏。现在，到了终场……准备自卫吧！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11853
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFAURAS_TRENCHESOFSHADOW\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr "你的仪式将你引至此处。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11855
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFAURAS_TRENCHESOFSHADOW\"]/text"
msgstr "抵达信标，你发现自己身处一片阴影之中……据说光环水晶就在这里，但外面什么也看不"
"见。虽然无法解释，你感觉被吸引到了异界典籍旁……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11858
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFAURAS_TRENCHESOFSHADOW\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "检查异界典籍。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11860
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFAURAS_TRENCHESOFSHADOW\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"当你靠近异界之书所在的房间时，注意到有光芒从门缝底下渗出。推门而入，你发现书"
"本本身正散发着炽烈的紫色光辉，神圣非凡……你感觉它正在将你往它那里牵引。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11862
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFAURAS_TRENCHESOFSHADOW\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "试着抵抗。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11864
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFAURAS_TRENCHESOFSHADOW\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "你试图抗拒，但……失败了。异界典籍将你吸入，吞噬了你，然后……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11866
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFAURAS_TRENCHESOFSHADOW\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "然后？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11868
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFAURAS_TRENCHESOFSHADOW\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你的名字是老西奥多·冯·法尔哈特，你是航行于“无赖之海”的最强战舰的船长。正是在"
"这片无赖之海中，隐藏着“阴影海沟”……一位预言家曾向你预言，那里将是你的葬身之地"
"。你现在正航行于其上，准备去出售你最近一批宝藏。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11872
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFAURAS_TRENCHESOFSHADOW\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续航行。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11874
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFAURAS_TRENCHESOFSHADOW\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "你与舵盘相处的时间之久，让它简直像是你的大副……不过，真正的大副正从桅杆瞭望台"
"上下来。他有什么要报告吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11876
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFAURAS_TRENCHESOFSHADOW\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "准备听他说。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11878
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFAURAS_TRENCHESOFSHADOW\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "他刚要开口，一颗炮弹便将他撕碎，血肉四溅。这可不是好兆头。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11880
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFAURAS_TRENCHESOFSHADOW\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "检查你的左舷。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11882
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFAURAS_TRENCHESOFSHADOW\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "不，那里什么也没有。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11884
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFAURAS_TRENCHESOFSHADOW\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "检查你的右舷。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11886
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFAURAS_TRENCHESOFSHADOW\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "是的，在那里……你星舰的右侧有另一艘船，正朝你的星舰开炮。你认出了他们的标志："
"该死的阴影海沟的鱼人……相当麻烦，因为你注定要死在这里。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11888
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFAURAS_TRENCHESOFSHADOW\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "接受你的命运。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11890
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFAURAS_TRENCHESOFSHADOW\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你离开舵盘，离开你那已化作一堆松散血肉的大副，退回到船长室……你的最终安息之地"
"。你从一个装满宝藏的箱子里翻出一块璀璨的水晶……你死前至少能做自己热爱的事：囤"
"积宝藏。你躺在床上，手握水晶，鱼人的炮火对你狂轰滥炸，你听着自己辉煌的星舰被"
"撕裂。是的，本该如此……然而，你希望……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11892
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFAURAS_TRENCHESOFSHADOW\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我希望……？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11894
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_CRYSTALOFAURAS_TRENCHESOFSHADOW\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你被一股猛烈的力量从异界典籍中弹了出来，砰的一声脸朝下摔在地上……刚才到底发生"
"了什么？你刚才在异界典籍里面……？还没等你真正回过神来，其他实体也被从书中弹了"
"出来……深渊潜者？！这些难道就是故事里的“鱼人”吗……？你刚要跑去拉响警报，却意识"
"到手里有什么东西……是光环水晶！尽管对其手段完全摸不着头脑，但你不得不承认，黑"
"暗之神确实知道如何上演一出好戏。现在，到了终场……准备自卫吧！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11924
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LEGENDARYCRYSTAL\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr "你的仪式将你引至此处。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11926
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LEGENDARYCRYSTAL\"]/text"
msgstr "抵达信标，你发现自己身处一片阴影之中……你如今已熟悉这套流程。坐在异界典籍旁，"
"你已准备好了五颗分离者水晶。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11929
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LEGENDARYCRYSTAL\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "等待异界典籍打开。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11931
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LEGENDARYCRYSTAL\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr "没等多久，异界典籍便发出空灵的光芒，最后一次，你被吸入它的书页之中……然后……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11933
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LEGENDARYCRYSTAL\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "然后……？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:11935
