#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:18121
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_LIST_SOULWEAVING_HUNGRY\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"魂疫黏团向你逼近，它的扭动加快了，你意识到了它的饥饿程度……它想拿你当下一餐。"
"你尽可能快地跑出房间，确保锁好身后的门，然后你听到它利用仅有的那点祭品，突变"
"为了一个魂疫空壳。只能希望这扇门能撑到你完成超光速跃迁。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:18126
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_LIST_SOULWEAVING_HUNGRY\"]/choice[3]/event/choice/text"
