msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_SOULFIRING_SHELL_FIGHT_LOSS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你意识到自己任务失败，低语，仍然异常平静，再次充满你的脑海：“……失败了……杀了我"
"们……杀了你……” 警报大作，一滩滩魂疫数据病毒在星舰内显形，并开始迅速突变成空壳"
"。你想它们对你不太高兴……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:18165
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_LIST_SOULFIRING_SHELL_FIGHT_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
