#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20051
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_CRYSTALLINECOMBAT_FIGHT_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"趁你终于有机会喘口气时，一种截然不同的感觉涌上心头——困惑。这些谐离精英所使用"
"的无人机，和他们平常的装备完全不同……这些无人机并非只是漆黑的金属造物，而是完"
"全被构成谐离神秘舰体装甲的同款暗影水晶所包裹。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20053
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_CRYSTALLINECOMBAT_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "检查这些奇异无人机的残骸。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20055
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_CRYSTALLINECOMBAT_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"幸好，残骸中还留有足够完整的无人机，可供你仔细查看……\n"
"\n"
"你原本是这么想的，可就在你触碰其中一架的瞬间，它立刻碎裂开来——连同它那微光闪"
"烁的甲壳一同崩解。一块飞溅而出的暗影水晶碎片擦过你的手臂，你眼睁睁看着一片相"
"似的水晶结构在你的皮肤上浮现……就在被划伤的位置。这东西暂时没有危险，用非接触"
"式工具就能轻松剥离，但它也给了你一个想法：如果你能用这种水晶包裹自己的谐离无"
"人机，会发生什么？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20059
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_CRYSTALLINECOMBAT_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"DISPARITY_LIBERATORTOG_DEFEND\"]/text"
msgstr "（解放者无人机）尝试将你的解放者封装于暗影水晶之中。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20061
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_CRYSTALLINECOMBAT_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"DISPARITY_LIBERATORTOG_DEFEND\"]/event/text"
msgstr "费了一番功夫，你抓起你的无人机，将其抵在那堆破碎的暗影水晶上……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20064
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_CRYSTALLINECOMBAT_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"DISPARITY_LIBERATORTOG_DEFEND\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

