#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20268
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_CRYSTALLINECOMBAT\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"dd_ritual_side_effect_triggered\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "那么，我们的解放就在前方——拿起武器！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20281
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr "你的仪式将你引至此处。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20283
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"抵达信标处，你置身于一片暗影之域……黑暗之神早已等候你的到来。但你还没来得及喘"
"息，你的飞船就险些撞上外界太空中的某个物体——一种巨大到超乎想象、形如巨树的结"
"构体，它笼罩了信标的这一整面。它那成百上千的枝杈，若你能如此称呼的话，在这片"
"黑暗中向远方延伸，远超你的视线所及。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20286
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_greattreedefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "敬畏地凝视着这棵巨树般的存在。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20288
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_greattreedefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你凝视着这雄伟的结构体，猛地从座椅上惊起——你意识到，它也在凝视着你。至少，你"
"确信是这样。在飞船上方不远处，你能清晰看到一只巨大的眼眸从巨树的主干上浮现。"
"在发现这一切后不久，一个低沉的女性声音直接在你脑海中响起：\n"
"\n"
"“是什么……将你带到这里，旅人？”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20292
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_greattreedefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我……呃……我是跟着一张星图来到这里的，我在寻找某种奖赏。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20294
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_greattreedefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"那只巨眼的瞳孔微微收缩，声音再次隆隆响起：\n"
"\n"
"“原来如此……你来了。和……他们所有人一样。是……她派你们来的吗？除了她……还会有谁？"
"”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20298
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_greattreedefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "她……？我不这么认为，不——我只是按照我那本，呃……其他部分都很正常的书里一张奇怪"
"的散页做的。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20300
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_greattreedefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"瞳孔此刻缓缓放大，你看着那只巨眼从你的飞船上移开，望向你周围幽暗的深渊。片刻"
"之后，你再次听见了这棵巨树的思绪：\n"
"\n"
"“我……想念她。她……已经很少再来了。可是……上一次她来的时候……她告诉我，我可以相信"
"你。我……愿意相信她的判断。即使……我无法相信你的话语。”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20304
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_greattreedefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我？我是说，是的！当然。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20306
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_greattreedefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"漫长的沉默降临，那棵巨树费力地转动着它巨大的眼眸：\n"
"\n"
"“是的……你。所有……来到这里的人。她所信任的……人。她曾……期盼的人。你……真的不记得"
"她了吗？”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20310
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_greattreedefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "很遗憾，我无法确定你说的是谁。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20312
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_greattreedefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你感到一阵不安，沉默再次笼罩四周……但紧接着，那只巨眼重新将目光聚焦在你的飞船"
"上，声音也变得无比温和：\n"
"\n"
"“没关系。我永远不会忘记她。即使你忘了。即使她忘了我。我记得她的承诺。我也记得"
"我的承诺。旅人……你说你是来寻找奖赏的，对吗？”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20316
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_greattreedefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "是的。我很喜欢奖赏。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20318
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_greattreedefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "它没有用言语回应，反而一道璀璨的蓝色光环开始在巨树庞大的表面流转，你的飞船船"
"体也随之亮起光芒。不知为何，你的船体似乎被完全修复了！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20321
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_greattreedefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "哇，呃……谢谢你，树之女士！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20323
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_greattreedefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"光环消散，巨树的瞳孔再次变得锐利：\n"
"\n"
"“那……并非善意。仅仅……是一个预防措施。我……不想不公地斩杀她的人。她……不会喜欢那"
"样。我……也不会。”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20327
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_greattreedefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "哦，好吧。等等——你刚才说斩杀？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20329
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_greattreedefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"那只巨眼闭上，一根比你飞船还要大上数倍的突起物以快得不可思议的速度从树干中猛"
"地伸出——朝你袭来，在你还没来得及做出任何反应之前就缠绕住了你的船体。随后你听"
"到一阵令人不安的碎裂声，有什么东西正在穿透飞船的内部……最终，那道声音在你脑海"
"中咆哮，意图昭然若揭：\n"
"\n"
"“证明……你配得上她许下的承诺。证明……你值得我的恩惠。”\n"
"\n"
"随后它再次陷入沉默，只剩下你的飞船被撕裂的声音——你必须尽快处理眼前这东西的所"
"作所为！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20339
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_greattreedefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/triggeredEvent/triggeredEventBox/tooltip"
msgstr "你的飞船墙壁内部传来一阵隆隆的声响……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20360
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_greattreedefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr "试着再次引起这棵巨树的注意。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20362
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_greattreedefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"尽管你竭尽全力集中意念，或是轰击它的树干，这棵巨树依旧纹丝不动。你仍无法确定"
"它是已经沉寂，还是仅仅不屑理会你这些微不足道的挑衅，但事实是，再次来到这里似"
"乎只是在浪费宝贵的时间。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20364
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_greattreedefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "星舰管理。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20368
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_greattreedefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "跳过。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20376
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_OHGODOHFUCK\"]/text"
msgstr "你拼命想要对眼前愈发危急的状况做出反应……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20381
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_OHGODOHFUCK\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20383
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_OHGODOHFUCK\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr "……可你还没来得及逃出多远，无数巨大如藤蔓般的根须就从飞船内部破土而出。如果你"
"想不出办法阻止这场疯狂，你注定会被撕成碎片！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20391
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//triggeredEvent[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_OHGODOHFUCK_THEYRECOMINGOUTOFTHEWALLLLLS\"]/triggeredEventBox/tooltip"
msgstr "你的飞船墙壁内部传来一阵隆隆的声响……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20400
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_OHGODOHFUCK_ITGETSEVENWORSE\"]/text"
msgstr "随着局势进一步恶化，你周围刺耳的嘈杂声莫名变得更加响亮……你必须抓紧时间！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20405
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_OHGODOHFUCK_ITGETSEVENWORSE\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "快点。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20411
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"那些如同根须般蔓延的侵袭主体已经死去，其余的外衍体也很快随之枯萎——外界那股巨"
"大的压迫感也一同消失了。你……在重重绝境中活了下来。接下来该怎么办？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20417
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_WIN\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "重重地松了一口气。刚才那场面……可真够吓人的。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20419
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_WIN\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你还精疲力竭、喘着气，外面那只巨眼再次睁开。你愤怒地瞪了它一眼，而巨树的声音"
"又强行钻进你的脑海：\n"
"\n"
"“你……值得。你……配得上。她知道了……一定会感到骄傲。虽然……我猜她内心深处……一直都"
"知道。”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20423
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "行吧，行吧——那我到底配得上什么？你刚刚可是把我扔进地狱里折腾了一通！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20425
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"仿佛是在回应你的质问，脚下残存的植被中突然冒出了一样东西……一块类似玻璃或水晶"
"的碎片。无论它是什么，都美得惊人。它璀璨的光芒为你周围的空间镀上了一层空灵的"
"光晕——在光谱中变幻出每一种绚丽的色彩。这东西……本身就是极致的华美。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20427
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "它……真的很美。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20429
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "那块美妙的水晶碎片……就在你的脚下。它在呼唤你，引诱你上前，投入它的怀抱。你只"
"需将它拾起……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20431
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "是的，我……我从未需要过其他任何东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20433
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "你凝视着碎片空灵的中心，完全迷失在它压倒性的辉煌中，周围的一切似乎都渐渐褪去…"
"…"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20435
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20437
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20441
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20443
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "弗尔，她真的走了吗？那你觉得我们在这里的时光……也只是短暂一瞬吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20445
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "等伊芙回来，重新做她最擅长的事，不过是时间问题罢了。追梦的人，终究还是会追梦"
"，five。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20447
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "或许吧，可是……我们的命运你就一点都不在意吗？万一我们再也见不到彼此了呢？我无"
"法想象seven能随心所欲地四处游荡——教皇陛下一定悲痛欲绝。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20449
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr ""
"现在把计划说出来，应该也没什么大碍了，对吧？伊芙一直……让我写这些奇怪的、像是"
"指令一样的东西。我完全不知道是为了什么，可是……她看起来非常确信，这些东西会送"
"到某个非常重要的人手里。一个能永远帮我们摆脱这该死困境的人。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20451
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "这些……确实是业余水平的素描啊，神枪手！就算用我的爪子握笔，也不会在纸上画得这"
"么……粗暴！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20453
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "哈！嘿，只要能把你逗笑——就算送不到任何人手里也没关系。这东西已经派上用场了，"
"不是吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20455
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"是吗？但愿seven这个计划，能成为她诸多计策里比较……靠谱的一个吧。这喧嚣之地虽不"
"是什么天堂圣域，可我们向来都是一同熬过这里的种种苦难。一想到从今往后我们必须"
"天各一方、从头开始……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20457
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我们又不会记得这破事，不是吗？至少……我希望不会。我敢说，那听上去也太孤单了。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20459
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"那么，最亲爱的four，究竟该由谁来记住这一切呢？若是我们连自我都迷失了，重逢……"
"难道不会变得不可能吗？那样的重逢，还会拥有同样的意义与价值吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20461
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我……不知道，five。不过伊芙看起来确实早就把一切都想好了。无论如何，我只能选择"
"相信她。因为，如果连她都不能相信，我还能相信谁呢？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20463
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "相信她，Four。为守护Seven的梦想而活下去——也去追寻你自己的，好吗？只要……你……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20465
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20467
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20469
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20471
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"刹那间，你的意识从这场陌生的对话中被强行抽离，一连串闪烁的幻象将你吞没。\n"
"\n"
"你看见一只螳螂，在冰冷坚硬的丝线操控下，随着无心的妄念起舞。\n"
"\n"
"接着，是一位深渊潜者，为生存奋力搏杀——直至永恒尽头，仍心怀希望。\n"
"\n"
"最后……一枚蔚蓝的印记。印记上缀着一道闪电，它灼刻进你的脑海，深深烙印在你的视"
"线之中。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20482
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "在当下的痛苦中煎熬。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20484
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“你……看见她了吗，可敬之人？这一切……值得吗？”\n"
"\n"
"你睁开双眼，失声尖叫，而外面那只巨眼只是一动不动地凝视着。“那么……我已经守住了"
"我的承诺，不是吗？她……也只需守住她的。”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20490
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "那到底是什么鬼东西？你到底在说什么？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20492
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"没有任何话语传来，你的脚下再次冒出了一个小小的东西……看起来，是一颗种子。你困"
"惑地盯着它看了片刻，随即转头望向外面的巨眼寻求答案——可它似乎已经重新闭上了。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20495
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "嘿，等等！我话还没说完呢！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20497
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"尽管你拼尽全力，外界的那个存在对你所有的沟通尝试都毫无反应。即便用武器去试探"
"，也完全徒劳无功。你不确定它是已经离去，还是仅仅在无视你，但……你觉得这已经无"
"关紧要了。你已经得到了你来此要寻找的东西，尽管它此刻依旧神秘而微弱……\n"
"\n"
"不过，你感觉那颗种子本身，并非困扰你最大的谜团。那块充满诱惑、如梦似幻的碎片"
"去了哪里？还有它强行灌入你脑海的那些幻象……你依然能感受到那枚奇异的蔚蓝印记，"
"深深灼烧在你的意识之中……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20501
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_PLANTSHOWDOWN_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "总有一天……我会找到答案。记住我的话，黑暗之神。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20540
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//ship[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_ULTIMACHALLENGE_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"这艘诡异的飞船在结构受损时不断闪烁。在最后一次发光后，飞船轰然爆炸，金属碎片"
"四散飞溅，无数道闪电般的光束冲向太空。你胜利了，可你的朋友们……又如何了呢？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20543
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//ship[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_ULTIMACHALLENGE_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20548
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//ship[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_ULTIMACHALLENGE_FIGHT\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"大臣的铠甲坠落，你看着它的飞船开始变得不稳定。飞船发出最后一次光芒后爆炸，金"
"属碎片四散飞溅，无数道闪电般的光束冲向太空。你胜利了，可你的朋友们……又如何了"
"呢？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20553
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//ship[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_ULTIMACHALLENGE_FIGHT\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20560
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_ULTIMACHALLENGE_FIGHT_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"一切平静下来后，你收到了另一条信息：\n"
"\n"
"终极能量：已超限\n"
"目标意愿：错误：整数溢出\n"
"伊芙琳指令：已覆盖\n"
"接收指令：载体指令\n"
"执行命令：协助：目标"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20569
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_ULTIMACHALLENGE_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "它还在运行？它真的是无法摧毁的吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20571
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_ULTIMACHALLENGE_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"仿佛在回应你的疑问，当那套铠甲出现在你身旁的房间时，你收到了第三条信息：\n"
"\n"
"终焉装甲：等待：目标指令"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20574
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_ULTIMACHALLENGE_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/event/crewMember"
msgstr "终焉之击"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20577
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_ULTIMACHALLENGE_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "尖叫着，攻击这该死的东西！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20579
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_ULTIMACHALLENGE_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "你将怒火尽数宣泄，猛力轰击着大臣的铠甲，却连让它挪动分毫都做不到，更别说留下"
"凹痕了。它就那样悬停在原地，仿佛在刻意嘲讽你。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20581
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_ULTIMACHALLENGE_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "你……对我的朋友们……做了什么……？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20583
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_ULTIMACHALLENGE_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "再也没有新的信息传来，那具铠甲也纹丝不动。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20585
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_ULTIMACHALLENGE_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "求求你，就……把他们带回来吧……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20587
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_ULTIMACHALLENGE_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "还是一片死寂，毫无回应。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20589
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_ULTIMACHALLENGE_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "你为什么在这里……？只是为了折磨我吗……？快滚吧……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20591
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_ULTIMACHALLENGE_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你话音刚落，便惊讶地看见那具铠甲重新运转起来；它只是转过身，随即从容地离开了"
"房间。你想起它最后那条信息……等待目标指令。这东西现在会听从你的命令了吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20593
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_ULTIMACHALLENGE_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我……呃……回来吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20595
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_ULTIMACHALLENGE_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"果然，铠甲走进房间，回到了它之前悬浮的位置。无论这副铠甲究竟是什么，它现在似"
"乎真的归你所有了。你心想，既然甩不掉它，至少可以加以利用，可是……你的朋友们呢"
"？暗神就是你唯一的仇恨目标吗？铠甲没有回应，只是在原地发出低沉的嗡鸣，仿佛在"
"嘲弄你所失去的一切……但或许，它也预示着你将获得的力量。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20617
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_ULTIMACHALLENGE\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr "在大臣的铠甲消失之后，你找到了这些坐标。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20619
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_ULTIMACHALLENGE\"]/text"
msgstr "抵达信标处，你发现自己身处一片奇异的云雾空域之中。偶尔有短暂的光芒闪烁，闪电"
"在云层之间穿梭，但除此之外，你没有发现任何值得注意的东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20622
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_ULTIMACHALLENGE\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "什么？那东西……为什么要带我来这里？我的朋友们在哪里？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20624
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_ULTIMACHALLENGE\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"纷乱的思绪在你脑海中翻腾，黑暗虚空中的一个物体突然吸引了你的注意。起初因为距"
"离遥远，很难看清，但当一道白光从它中心亮起时，你立刻认出了那是什么。那是大臣"
"的铠甲，漂浮在宇宙中……等着你。你还没来得及做出反应，一阵声响便激起了你的怒火—"
"—你的飞船收到了一条直接发来的信息。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20626
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_ULTIMACHALLENGE\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "打开信息。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20628
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_ULTIMACHALLENGE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"信息内容如下：\n"
"\n"
"终焉装甲：已上线\n"
"目标存在：无效请求\n"
"执行指令：目标清除"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20634
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_ULTIMACHALLENGE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "这套装甲……还能交流？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20636
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_ULTIMACHALLENGE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"仿佛是在回应你，外面的铠甲开始散发出一缕空灵的光芒，穿透了你周围的云层。光芒"
"越来越亮，直到一道强光占据了你的视线——那种感觉你已经很熟悉了……等你再次恢复视"
"觉时，铠甲已经消失，取而代之的是一艘你从未见过的飞船。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20639
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_ULTIMACHALLENGE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "它想开战是吧？那就来吧。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20641
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_ULTIMACHALLENGE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"闪电从那艘飞船中劈出，堪堪擦过你的飞船，你这才意识到，这艘诡异的飞船竟是由纯"
"粹的电流构成……至少，是某种异界能量。它不断逼近，又一道闪电从你飞船旁掠过。做"
"好准备！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_ddrituals.xml:20645
msgid ""
"data/events_special_ddrituals.xml$//event[@name=\"DDRITUALS_QUESTS_ULTIMACHALLENGE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"
